data.description: Come check out this CHARMING and SPACIOUS 2Bedroom/2.5 Bathroom + OFFICE in the BEAUTIFUL SUN LAKES!  Walking in you will notice tons of NATURAL LIGHT, CLEAN and FRESH feeling with neutral colors, HUGE kitchen with LOADS of counterspace, OPEN are for both Formal dining and kitchen dining area.  You'll ENJOY the large MASTER SUITE which has a LUXURIOUS bathroom including large walk in closet, Jacuuzi tub and plenty of room.  Brand new a/c units, new r/o system, soft water, central vacuum...this house has it all!! Seller is willing to leave home 80% furnished!
